body:
I know this title might sound a bit miss leading and it is a little, the people who said this thought they were being funny and joking around but really weren&#039;t.

CHAMP SELECT- &quot;someone said omg why r u going ahri jg ??? autistic&quot; (i went ahri jg because I was going to swap with my mid but he decided not to and we had a hec mid, and this was a normal match)
I said you should say that its really offensive and not something you should joke around about.

GAME- the same person says in all chat report this autistic ahri and hec
I said &quot;don&#039;t say that&quot;
 then the two other players (not the hec) say stuff like &quot;idc if you&#039;re offended by it I can do what I like idk why you would care&quot;
I said &quot;idk maybe I have autism&quot; (Asperger&#039;s syndrome)
&quot;it shows,&quot; one of them said
later on in the game near the end, one of the players say &quot;people with autism or stupid and a waste of space&quot;
I said, &quot;oh you&#039;re a Nazi, are you?&quot;
someone said &quot;what?&quot;
&quot;Hitler ordered the death of thousands of people with mental illnesses&quot;
&quot;well then I agree with Hitler people with autism don&#039;t deserve to live&quot;
another person said &quot;you should just kys no one will care anyway&quot;

I did send a report and nothing happened I just feel people telling someone to kill themselves, or die, or being pro nazi and sharing it is wrong especially when you say it to someone when it&#039;s out of their control

riot if u want their names just ask me for them I really want to see them punished.
